item.title: A Fun Satirical Song
item.dc:creator: Caligula
item.description:
You know things are really bad in New Zealand when even the BBC is reporting on how bad things have become"
You can't make a living in New Zealand. There is no living. You just go backwards. You don't get a choice if you want live, you have to move, or New Zealand has to change. I want a future for my children and there is none in New Zealand,"

BBC report in full

item.title: A Fun Satirical Song
item.dc:creator: Caligula
item.description:
A satirical song about the many policy failures of Jacinda Ardern. I don't agree with everything in the song, but even if you only agree with a few of the points it shows just how despicable a creature Jacinda Ardern is.

Look at me song
